hotel_data.name: St. Regis San Francisco
hotel_data.hotel_description: Featuring a full service spa, an indoor infinity pool and an on-site restaurant, this luxury hotel is located in the SOMA District of San Francisco. A flat-screen TV is included in each guest room. Union Square is 8 minutes’ walk away. A luxurious bathroom with a soaking tub and a TV is featured in all guest rooms at St. Regis San Francisco. Each elegantly decorated room boasts a minibar and a DVD player. Guests of St. Regis San Francisco can enjoy breakfast, lunch and dinner at the Grill restaurant. The restaurant features grilled meats, fish, burgers and an oyster bar in an intimate setting. Signature cocktails and a bar menu are offered at St. Regis Lobby Lounge. Located on-site, Remede Spa provides separate whirlpools, steam rooms and saunas for men and women. Guests can enjoy chilled champagne and handmade truffles before seeing a spa therapist. Information regarding area events and activities can be requested at the concierge desk. The St. Regis San Francisco is across the street from Yerba Buena Gardens. AT&T Park is 1.6 km away.

hotel_data.name: The Mosser Hotel
hotel_data.hotel_description: This San Francisco hotel, built in 1913, mixes contemporary conveniences with historical design. The hotel features an on-site state-of-the-art recording studio and rooms with access to free WiFi. Guestrooms at The Mosser Hotel include a bathrobe and hairdryer. Some rooms offer a private bathroom with bath amenities. Guests can enjoy American comfort food at the Keystone. The restaurant has a 12-seat communal table and serves high quality spirits with rare flavour combinations. Two Happy Hours and weekend brunch are offered at the Keystone. The Hotel Mosser is within a 5-minute walk of Moscone Convention Center. The Powell Street BART Station is within a 3-minute walk of the hotel and allows for easy access of San Francisco attractions including Fisherman’s Wharf and Chinatown. Parking is available for an extra fee.

hotel_data.name: Inn at Union Square, a Greystone Hotel
hotel_data.hotel_description: This European-style hotel is located 1 block from Union Square Park and 4 blocks from the Powell Street BART Station. It offers rooms with a flat-screen TV and free WiFi. Valet parking and 24-hour concierge services are available at this Union Square hotel. The Cable Car Museum and Chinatown are both 10 minutes' walk from Inn at Union Square. Fisherman’s Wharf is 20 minutes' cable car ride away.

hotel_data.name: Staybridge Suites San Francisco Airport
hotel_data.hotel_description: Located 5 minutes’ drive from San Francisco International Airport, Staybridge Suites San Francisco Airport offers free airport shuttles. This completely non-smoking hotel offers all-suite accommodation furnished with full kitchens and free WiFi. Guests can relax in the pool and hot tub. Guest accommodation at Staybridge Suites San Francisco Airport includes a flat-screen cable satellite HDTV, a microwave, a full refrigerator and a dishwasher. For business travelers each suite includes a work desk with a chair and convenient electrical outlets. Local phone calls are free. San Francisco Airport Staybridge Suites provides a number of exceptional services, including a free breakfast buffet and free evening reception on Monday, Tuesday and Wednesday between the hours of 17:30 and 19:30. A 24-hour fitness centre, a 24-hour business centre and guest self-laundry facilities are located on site. Offering service to Central San Francisco locations, San Bruno BART Station is 2 minutes’ drive from the property. San Francisco State University is 15 minutes’ drive from Staybridge Suites San Francisco Airport. South San Francisco Convention Center is 10 minutes’ drive away.

hotel_data.name: Travelodge by Wyndham San Francisco Bay
hotel_data.hotel_description: Less than 1.6 km away from Fisherman's Wharf and offering easy access to popular San Francisco city centre attractions, this conveniently located motel features a 24-hour multi-lingual front desk. Free WiFi is available in all guest rooms. A cable TV, a work desk and coffee-making facilities are offered in all air-conditioned rooms at Travelodge by Wyndham by the Bay. A hairdryer is provided in the private bathroom. Travelodge by Wyndham by the Bay is only minutes from the city's historic cable cars and the famous Lombard Street, also known as the "crookedest" street in the world. Chinatown is 10 minutes’ drive away. The iconic Golden Gate Bridge is 5 km away.

hotel_data.name: Hilton Garden Inn San Francisco/Oakland Bay Bridge
hotel_data.hotel_description: Hilton Garden Inn San Francisco/Oakland Bay Bridge is located just off I-80 and I-580. It features an on-site restaurant and lounge, a complimentary shuttle within a 4.8 km radius, and a modern fitness centre. The warmly decorated rooms offer free WiFi access, a flat-screen TV, a microwave, and a refrigerator. The San Francisco/Oakland Bay Bridge Hilton Garden Inn has a hot tub. A 24-hour front desk, business center, and ATM are also available. The on-site Great American Grill serves traditional American dishes for breakfast, lunch, and dinner. The Pavilion Lounge offers drinks and appetizers. An on-site convenience mart, the Pavilion Pantry, sells snacks and microwaveable meals. Bay Street shopping and dining is just 0.8 km from Hilton Garden Inn San Francisco. Claremont Country Club is 8 km away. Oakland International Airport is 19 km away.

Great American Grill, located on site, serves contemporary cuisine for breakfast and dinner. Hilton Garden Inn San Francisco is 8 miles from downtown San Francisco. Oyster Point Marina is only one mile away.

hotel_data.name: DoubleTree by Hilton San Francisco Airport North
hotel_data.hotel_description: Offering a free transfer service to San Francisco International Airport, this hotel provides a restaurant and a indoor splash pool. Free WiFi is provided in all rooms. Union Square is 15 minutes’ drive away. Styled in modern decor, each air-conditioned room offers ergonomic desk chair, a flat-screen TV and free toiletries in the en suite bathroom. A coffee machine is also provided at DoubleTree by Hilton San Francisco Airport North. Select suites feature a spacious seating area. WhiteCaps Drinks + Eats, located on site, is open for breakfast, lunch and dinner. Boasting bay views, Whitecaps Drinks + Eats features indoor and outdoor seating. This restaurant offers Californian cuisine and provides a full bar. A poolside hot tub is also featured at DoubleTree by Hilton Hotel San Francisco Airport North. A fitness centre is located on site as well as a 24-hour business centre for guests. AT&T Park, home of the San Francisco Giants Baseball Team, is 13 km away. Fisherman's Wharf is 20 minutes’ drive away from DoubleTree by Hilton San Francisco Airport North.

hotel_data.name: Music City Hotel/Hostel
hotel_data.hotel_description: Music City, a bold entertainment company bringing artists together to ignite the soul of local music culture. An immersive experience with access to rehearsal studios, and the world’s largest Bay Area music gallery. Bookings help support local musicians. Free WiFi is offered. The Mission District is 3.5 km away. Linens, toiletries, and towels are provided to all guests. Select private rooms include an en suite bathroom. All rooms include free music rehearsal time. Free coffee/tea and fresh fruit are offered daily as well as free luggage storage.Airport drop off services can be arranged by Music City Hotel/Hostel. Daily maid service is included. North Beach is 2.9 km away from this accommodation. San Francisco’s Haight Ashbury District is 15 minutes’ drive away, while Japantown is a 15 minutes' walk away.

hotel_data.name: Hotel Kabuki, a Joie de Vivre Hotel
hotel_data.hotel_description: Located in San Francisco’s Japantown, this elegant hotel is connected to the Nihonmachi Mall and blends Eastern and Western design. It features on-site dining and an indoor garden with a fishpond. Free WiFi is available at the property. Blending traditional Japanese style decor with modern amenities, rooms at Hotel Kabuki, a Joie de Vivre Hotel offer a flat-screen Smart HDTV with streaming apps, a spacious bathroom with a walk-in shower, guest robes and boutique bath amenities. A mini-refrigerator and a coffee machine are also provided in all guest rooms. The Bar at Hotel Kabuki features Japanese whisky, sake and beer, as well as an assortment of international-inspired light snacks. The bar offers a Monday through Friday Happy Hour. The on-site fitness centre with state-of-the-art equipment is open 24 hours a day. Valet parking, laundry services and free newspapers are available. Shops and cafes at San Francisco's Union Square are 10 minutes' bus ride from Hotel Kabuki, a Joie de Vivre Hotel. San Francisco's Chinatown is 2 km from the property.
